28:21.040 --> 28:22.960
-They're digging a tunnel.
-What?

28:23.120 --> 28:27.920
Yes, they have a lot of plastic explosive
and petrol containers.

28:28.080 --> 28:30.120
-Stand up!
-It'll be a slaughter.

28:30.800 --> 28:33.520
There's one way: contact the police
and guide them in the assault.

28:33.640 --> 28:36.320
I've got a phone in my office,
in the coat.

28:37.440 --> 28:38.880
