28:41.760 --> 28:43.720
-I'll go.
-No, no, no.

28:49.440 --> 28:50.800
There's always a hero...

28:53.240 --> 28:55.400
who thinks he can save the others.

28:57.560 --> 28:58.760
Who thinks...

29:01.680 --> 29:04.240
