he's associated with the robbery

29:31.040 --> 29:32.040
of a mansion in Geneva.

29:32.200 --> 29:34.320
He's got a warrant issued by the Interpol.

29:34.800 --> 29:39.720
So I'd like to give him
the chance to step forward

29:39.880 --> 29:42.400
so you can all thank him.

29:42.920 --> 29:44.920
And also give me that phone.

29:45.160 --> 29:48.480
He must have visited the Casa de la Moneda
to study the alarm systems.

29:49.800 --> 29:52.400
Check the hard drives
of the security company.

29:53.440 --> 29:56.640
With a bit of luck, maybe he went there
with some other gang members.

29:56.800 --> 29:57.680
Helsinki.

29:58.520 --> 29:59.560
Undress him.

29:59.920 --> 30:02.200
-Come on.
-Are you sick or what?

30:03.120 --> 30:04.160
Pay attention.

30:06.080 --> 30:08.080
Come on, take off your shirt.

30:09.800 --> 30:11.680
-Come on.
-It was one of you.

30:16.520 --> 30:19.080
I don't know who it was.

30:22.480 --> 30:24.440
Denver, undress her.

30:35.440 --> 30:38.200
You recorded a video

30:40.000 --> 30:41.800
