Listen, the inspector is coming out.

33:41.320 --> 33:42.960
"Move the paparazzi away."

34:09.120 --> 34:12.440
Leave the boxes on the ground
and go back really slowly.

34:43.960 --> 34:46.600
"I've got a phone
in my office, in the coat."

34:53.240 --> 34:54.400
