35:07.520 --> 35:09.000
The medicine.

35:30.600 --> 35:31.520
I'm going...

35:32.120 --> 35:33.040
Hey!

35:34.200 --> 35:35.080
May I?

35:41.840 --> 35:42.880
Sit down.

35:44.680 --> 35:45.920
