35:58.560 --> 36:00.240
The medicine is here.

36:03.640 --> 36:04.880
Hand them out.

36:10.120 --> 36:11.800
-I'm going to sit down.
-Wait.

36:15.200 --> 36:16.480
Come outside.

36:18.280 --> 36:19.520
Come outside.

36:49.200 --> 36:51.600
