in the Fábrica Nacional de Moneda...."

37:17.600 --> 37:19.240
They're not leaving that place, right?

37:21.160 --> 37:22.040
Those people, I mean.

37:22.120 --> 37:24.760
You must be desperate
to do something like that, right?

37:25.200 --> 37:27.320
That's what makes them so dangerous.

37:27.800 --> 37:29.840
No, but they don't want to hurt anybody.

37:31.400 --> 37:32.800
Well, that's what they said.

37:33.760 --> 37:36.400
So they wouldn't be armed,
don't you think?

37:37.360 --> 37:38.960
Sure, I guess you're right.

37:40.520 --> 37:42.080
But you don't try to rob

37:42.160 --> 37:44.800
