of these motherfuckers, or me.

40:26.920 --> 40:29.760
-Are you going to screw up my life?
-Life gets screwed up very easily.

40:29.840 --> 40:31.640
One day you're working smoothly,

40:32.240 --> 40:34.480
four lunatics with Dalí masks come in,

40:35.560 --> 40:38.320
