and everything goes wrong.

40:38.800 --> 40:41.080
This screws up your life.

40:44.840 --> 40:46.040
Not a baby.

40:47.160 --> 40:50.000
What do you know about what screws me
up? What do you know?

40:52.640 --> 40:54.000
My mother wanted to abort me.

40:55.440 --> 40:56.400
But first...

40:56.920 --> 40:59.000
she felt the need to snort
some of the blow my dad had to sell

40:59.080 --> 41:00.600
so they could pay for the abortion.

41:01.200 --> 41:04.920
And the municipal police
arrested her in a shitty portico.

41:05.920 --> 41:08.840
I was born among the jail,
the drugs and the police.

41:09.840 --> 41:10.920
And what do you know?

41:14.560 --> 41:17.640
Because it seems your job
is not one adventure after another,

41:17.720 --> 41:19.560
and when you go out
it isn't a party, either.

41:19.640 --> 41:21.160
-Or do you do "kilates"?
-Pilates...

41:21.320 --> 41:23.200
So I was right.
And you go for a drink on Friday.

41:23.280 --> 41:25.760
Fucking shit, girl,
another plan screwed up due to the baby.

41:25.840 --> 41:28.200
Who do you go out with?
Where are your friends?

41:28.280 --> 41:31.440
I'll tell you. At home, with their babies.

41:31.520 --> 41:34.400
Do they look screwed up? No, right?

41:35.360 --> 41:38.200
What crazy thing do you do
that you can't do with a baby?

41:41.320 --> 41:43.800
If his father is an arsehole
and he misses it, that's better,

41:43.880 --> 41:46.400
