with a little water?

42:02.360 --> 42:03.960
Abortion is a private thing, right?

42:05.320 --> 42:08.240
Women decide,
but not in front of everybody.

42:10.000 --> 42:11.040
Anyway, I'm...

42:12.320 --> 42:14.560
I'll think about it
until we get out of here.

42:23.680 --> 42:24.720
Wonderful.

42:27.760 --> 42:31.160
I'm glad you want to continue
with the pregnancy. Really.

42:33.320 --> 42:36.200
Now go back to the office with the others.

43:37.640 --> 43:39.600
Did you just come from a stag party?

43:41.040 --> 43:42.120
Or were you going there?

43:47.880 --> 43:50.160
"That wasn't the first time
Berlin put his hand

43:50.240 --> 43:51.920
in the knickers of an honest woman,

43:53.000 --> 43:55.840
but it'd be the first time
he'd take it out so soon.

43:56.600 --> 43:58.960
Maybe Mónica would have preferred
him to let himself go,

43:59.040 --> 44:01.120
follow his instinct
and forget about the phone

44:01.200 --> 44:04.520
that had rung between her legs,
but it wasn't so ."

44:08.600 --> 44:09.560
Denver.

44:12.240 --> 44:15.880
