46:02.400 --> 46:05.880
What's up? Jesus, Tokyo, Tokyo. Tokyo!

46:06.440 --> 46:08.160
Jesus, go and find Berlin.

46:44.840 --> 46:47.920
"Listen to me. If anybody
touches him again,"

46:48.080 --> 46:49.640
I swear to God that the next shot

46:49.720 --> 46:53.000
