47:08.320 --> 47:09.680
"Helsinki, put the gun down."

47:09.760 --> 47:11.800
What are you doing?

47:13.000 --> 47:13.880
Helsinki.

47:19.600 --> 47:20.720
Helsinki.

47:22.120 --> 47:23.200
Put the gun down.

47:30.080 --> 47:32.000
Don't do it, please.

47:32.080 --> 47:33.920
Why did you have to get
that fucking phone?

47:34.000 --> 47:34.880
Sorry.

47:35.040 --> 47:36.760
Why the hell did you have to trick me?

47:37.280 --> 47:38.440
Tokyo...

47:39.640 --> 47:40.800
Rio, don't!

47:42.160 --> 47:45.840
Where do you think you're going?
You did more than enough today.

47:46.440 --> 47:47.320
Helsinki.

47:57.800 --> 47:59.720
Do you know what will happen
if I don't kill you?

48:02.480 --> 48:04.280
-They'll kill me.
-No...

48:05.200 --> 48:06.920
