48:18.960 --> 48:22.040
were pointing at me,
reality fell like a concrete slab

48:22.120 --> 48:25.560
and I knew the five months
during which I had believed in something

48:25.640 --> 48:26.920
were over."

48:27.160 --> 48:29.640
Your love story has fucked up
your escape plan.

